long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play Impossible Game is an interesting game right on the chrome extension with gameplay that requires high concentration and skill. By clicking on the game to start, moving forward, backward, up and down to pass the continuously moving horizontal bars, your job is not to let the bars hit and enter the correct remaining purple box to win.
